  m_Name: Chest-KeyTutorial
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  header: Keys and Chests
  description: To uncover the secrets of each map, you'll need to unlock the chests
    scattered across it. These chests contain valuable items that will aid you on
    your journey. However, you'll need a key to open them, so be sure to keep an
    eye out for one as you explore. The treasures inside could make all the difference!
